name: CliKintoneTest-14 Should return the error message when no authorized information
fullName: features/common.feature#CliKintoneTest-14 Should return the error message when no authorized information

steps.name: When I run the command with args "record export --base-url $$TEST_KINTONE_BASE_URL --app 1"
Then I should get the exit code is non-zero
And The output error message should match with the pattern: "\[401\] \[CB_AU01\] Please login."

labels.name: suite
labels.value: CliKintoneTest-14 Should return the error message when no authorized information
